# Routing And Navigation

- Use Expo Router file-based routes for app-level navigation in `app/`.
- Keep `app/_layout.tsx` as global provider/root-stack wiring only.
- Nested React Navigation is allowed only for isolated feature flows (for example bottom-sheet internal stack).
- Do not mix router and nested navigator responsibilities in one component.
- Keep route params typed and stable; avoid ad-hoc string keys.
- Update navigation behavior docs when snap points or sheet flow semantics change.
